><div class="spacer-xl-start-copy"><p class="copy-medium headline">Commercials</p></div><div class="section-tabs"><div class="container-w3-5 gutter-outside"><div class="tabs-portfolio"><div data-current="Captain D&#x27;s" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="500" data-duration-out="500" class="tabs w-tabs"><div class="tabs-menu-wrapper w-tab-menu"><a data-w-tab="Captain D&#x27;s" class="tabs-nav-item _01 w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current"><div class="tabs-nav-text">Captain D&#x27;s</div><div class="tabs-nav-background"></div></a><a data-w-tab="Aflac" class="tabs-nav-item _02 w-inline-block w-tab-link"><div class="tabs-nav-text">Aflac</div></a><a data-w-tab="National Debt Relief" class="tabs-nav-item _03 w-inline-block w-tab-link"><div class="tabs-nav-text">National Debt Relief</div></a></div><div class="tabs-content-wrapper w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Captain D&#x27;s" class="tab-content-item w-tab-pane w--tab-active"><div class="tab-content-inner"><img sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a74c8b2d15b2e0c8b393_VS--CaptainDsDaymondDealv12-Conformmp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a74c8b2d15b2e0c8b393_VS--CaptainDsDaymondDealv12-Conformmp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a74c8b2d15b2e0c8b393_VS--CaptainDsDaymondDealv12-Conformmp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a74c8b2d15b2e0c8b393_VS--CaptainDsDaymondDealv12-Conformmp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a74c8b2d15b2e0c8b393_VS--CaptainDsDaymondDealv12-Conformmp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D%20(2).jpg 1920w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a74c8b2d15b2e0c8b393_VS--CaptainDsDaymondDealv12-Conformmp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D%20(2).jpg" class="tab-content-image"/></div><div class="tab-text"><p class="copy-medium">Captain D’s teamed up with Daymond to create a new value proposition and product offering for the seafood giant including a new hand-breaded Chick-N-D’s and a $5.99 Meal Deal offering. Captain D&#x27;s saw a notable increase in brand awareness among the 25-44 age demographics and extended beyond digital, reaching audiences on linear TV across 20 key markets, including Atlanta, Nashville, Birmingham, Jacksonville, and major southern regions.<br/><br/></p></div></div><div data-w-tab="Aflac" class="tab-content-item w-tab-pane"><div class="tab-content-inner"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a8c8eebfb0a3bf8cd477_VS--CareerSwitchers-Dropbox-0%E2%80%9900%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a8c8eebfb0a3bf8cd477_VS--CareerSwitchers-Dropbox-0%E2%80%9900%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a8c8eebfb0a3bf8cd477_VS--CareerSwitchers-Dropbox-0%E2%80%9900%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a8c8eebfb0a3bf8cd477_VS--CareerSwitchers-Dropbox-0%E2%80%9900%E2%80%9D%20(2)-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a8c8eebfb0a3bf8cd477_VS--CareerSwitchers-Dropbox-0%E2%80%9900%E2%80%9D%20(2).jpg 1920w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764a8c8eebfb0a3bf8cd477_VS--CareerSwitchers-Dropbox-0%E2%80%9900%E2%80%9D%20(2).jpg" class="tab-content-image"/></div><div class="tab-text"><p class="copy-medium">In collaboration with Daymond John, we supported Aflac&#x27;s Make Your Mark Campaign for recruiting the next generation of agents. Aflac was faced with trying to attract a more diverse customer base and after pulling that thread further, a recruitment campaign was birthed to find diverse Aflac brokers to jumpstart their new career as an insurance agent, gain more diverse customers, and better serve the existing Aflac community.</p></div></div><div data-w-tab="National Debt Relief" class="tab-content-item w-tab-pane"><div class="tab-content-inner"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D-p-2000.jpg 2000w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D-p-2600.jpg 2600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D-p-3200.jpg 3200w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D.jpg 3840w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/6764b965711800e58879fd17_VS--STAMP-OF-APPROVALMETAHORIZONTAL60-SECNO-CAPTIONSV2mp4-0%E2%80%9908%E2%80%9D.jpg" class="tab-content-image"/></div><div class="tab-text"><p class="copy-medium">In partnership with National Debt Relief, Daymond and NDR teamed up to help curate an story that authentically reaches individuals facing financial challenges. By aligning Daymond&#x27;s personal pitfalls with spending debt and starting FUBU&#x27;s success off of personal credits, we crafted a campaign that not only educates but also empowers consumers to take control of their financial future.<br/></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><section class="section-bed"><div class="container-brands-bed"><div class="bed-component"><img class="bed-logo" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo.png" width="275" height="Auto" alt="" style="opacity:0" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 275px" data-w-id="92c59102-f6a0-7f1d-e09f-f43a917000fe" loading="lazy" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo-p-1080.png 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo-p-1600.png 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo-p-2000.png 2000w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo-p-2600.png 2600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7cf_852221dd8bf073fc06ff84d81eb48556_BED-Logo-p-3200.png 3200w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f3a4ca9ef014e1b91f8308/67ccadec503564721574f7